name: com.android.printspooler.ui.AddPrinterActivity
description: This is an activity for adding a printer or. It consists of a list fed from three adapters: #mEnabledServicesAdapter for all enabled services. If a service has an PrintServiceInfo#getAddPrintersActivityName() add printer activity this is started when the item is clicked. #mDisabledServicesAdapter for all disabled services. Once clicked the settings page for this service is opened. #mRecommendedServicesAdapter for a link to all services. If this item is clicked the market app is opened to show all print services.
